Symbol.Script_VL:
hideparameter all "A", "B", "zzyzx"
call "FM_types" parameters all
values{2} "iChairModelStyle" CHAIRMODEL_STYLE1, `Стиль 1`, CHAIRMODEL_STYLE2, `Стиль 2`, CHAIRMODEL_STYLE3, `Стиль 3`, CHAIRMODEL_STYLE4, `Стиль 4`, CHAIRMODEL_STYLE5, `Стиль 5`, CHAIRMODEL_STYLE6, `Стиль 6`, CHAIRMODEL_STYLE7, `Стиль 7` values{2} "gs_detlevel_3D_m" DLEV3D_DETAILED, `Детальный`, DLEV3D_SIMPLE, `Простой`, DLEV3D_OFF, `Откл.`
call "2dDetailLevel" parameters gs_detlevel_2D = gs_detlevel_2D, gs_detlevel_2D_m = gs_detlevel_2D_m, returned_parameters det2D
if gs_detlevel_2D_m <> 4 then HIDEPARAMETER "gs_SymbolType" lock "gs_SymbolType", "gs_SymbolType_m" endif
call "fa_ChairSymbol" parameters all stSymbolTypes = stSymbolTypes
if iChairModelStyle <> CHAIRMODEL_STYLE3 then lock "gs_armrest" hideparameter "gs_armrest" endif
IF gs_cont_pen=0 THEN parameters gs_cont_pen=4 IF gs_fill_pen=0 THEN PARAMETERS gs_fill_pen=19
values "gs_resol" range [3,)
if gs_detlevel_3D_m = DLEV3D_SIMPLE then lock "gs_resol" hideparameter "gs_resol" endif
if gs_detlevel_3D_m = DLEV3D_OFF then lock "gs_resol", "gs_shadow", "gs_full_edit" hideparameter "gs_resol", "gs_shadow", "gs_full_edit" endif
! --- Setting range for ZZYZX and seat height
_minSeatHeight = 0.1 if iChairModelStyle = CHAIRMODEL_STYLE7 then _minSeatHeight = 0.25 _minBackrestHeight = 0 if iChairModelStyle = CHAIRMODEL_STYLE1 then _minBackrestHeight = 0.32 if iChairModelStyle = CHAIRMODEL_STYLE2 then _minBackrestHeight = 0.15 if iChairModelStyle = CHAIRMODEL_STYLE3 then _minBackrestHeight = 0.25 if iChairModelStyle = CHAIRMODEL_STYLE4 then _minBackrestHeight = 0.15 if iChairModelStyle = CHAIRMODEL_STYLE5 then _minBackrestHeight = 0.15 if iChairModelStyle = CHAIRMODEL_STYLE6 then _minBackrestHeight = 0.15 if iChairModelStyle = CHAIRMODEL_STYLE7 then _minBackrestHeight = 0.25
values "ZZYZX" range [_minSeatHeight + _minBackrestHeight, )
if iChairModelStyle = CHAIRMODEL_STYLE1 then !gs_seat_height is a locked parameter in Style 1, always set by ZZYZX gs_seat_height = ZZYZX - _minBackrestHeight parameters gs_seat_height = gs_seat_height lock "gs_seat_height" else values "gs_seat_height" range [_minSeatHeight, ZZYZX - _minBackrestHeight] endif
!!! *** Default Symbolic Value
IF GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "iChairModelStyle" THEN IF iChairModelStyle = CHAIRMODEL_STYLE1 AND gs_detlevel_2D_m = 4 THEN PARAMETERS gs_SymbolType = `Круглый со Спинкой` IF iChairModelStyle = CHAIRMODEL_STYLE4 AND gs_detlevel_2D_m = 4 THEN PARAMETERS gs_SymbolType = `Круглый со Спинкой` IF iChairModelStyle = CHAIRMODEL_STYLE7 AND gs_detlevel_2D_m = 4 THEN PARAMETERS gs_SymbolType = `Круглый со Спинкой`
IF iChairModelStyle = CHAIRMODEL_STYLE2 AND gs_detlevel_2D_m = 4 THEN PARAMETERS gs_SymbolType = `Прямоугольный со Спинкой 1` IF iChairModelStyle = CHAIRMODEL_STYLE3 AND gs_detlevel_2D_m = 4 THEN PARAMETERS gs_SymbolType = `Прямоугольный со Спинкой 1` IF iChairModelStyle = CHAIRMODEL_STYLE5 AND gs_detlevel_2D_m = 4 THEN PARAMETERS gs_SymbolType = `Прямоугольный со Спинкой 1` IF iChairModelStyle = CHAIRMODEL_STYLE6 AND gs_detlevel_2D_m = 4 THEN PARAMETERS gs_SymbolType = `Прямоугольный со Спинкой 1` ENDIF
